              "free_text": [
                " The total uncertainty in energy",
                "calculation range from 1.4% at 67 MeV to 29% at 7. MeV.",
                " This uncertainty includes:",
                "  * The error in the incident beam energy  - 1%",
                "  * The error in the range values  - 1%",
                "  * The error in the Al-target density  - 0.1%",
                "  * The error in the Al-target thickness (weighing",
                "     errors)   - 0.1%",
                "The excitation functions reported here have energy",
                "uncertainties ranging from +-1. MeV at 67.5 MeV,",
                "to +-2. MeV at 7. MeV."
              ]
            },
